In dynec::tracer

?

Struct dynec::tracer::Aggregate

source · 
pub struct Aggregate<T>(pub T);
Expand description

Groups multiple tracers into a tuple and dispatches each call to them in serial.

Tuple Fields§

§0: T

A tuple of child tracers to execute in serial.
